title: VA -Mod Mania 2010
description:
Mod Mania is a two CD collection of classic mod recordings, bringing together the biggest artists from both phases of the mod scene. The album includes hits from The Small Faces, The Who, The Kinks, The Spencer Davis Group and the biggest Northern Soul Classics, through to The Lambrettas, The Jam, Secret Affair and The Purple Hearts.
